entry.title: SPUCB10
entry.summary:
Vendor: STARMAXDESIGN
Type:
Price: 0.00

PU components are a new type of building material made of polyurethane materials. It has excellent heat insulation, preservation, sound absorption, fire prevention, and other characteristics. While ensuring aesthetics, PU components also have the advantage of being ultra-lightweight.

Compared with traditional building materials, PU components are simple to manufacture and easy to install, which can significantly improve the efficiency of building construction and save the cost of building materials. The thickness of the PU component can reach up to 6cm, and the three-dimensional effect of imitating stone is excellent. You can customize Its color and style on demand, and widely used in construction fields such as walls, roofs, doors and windows, wall panels, partitions, floors, and ceilings.
